{
  "stem": "10181.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But I remember the-- the Greeks hiding in our barracks because they were afraid.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they didn't go out to roll call because they were afraid of the Germans.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So we hid them in the barracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I mean, I didn't, but they were hidden by-- by some of our people in the barracks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And of course, they kept a low profile because they were afraid that the Germans would take them away from Bergen-Belsen and send them somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then-- this was at the time already of Kramer, OK?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, aside from the new people coming into our camp, people were coming from east-- from the east on those famous death-- or infamous death marches-- or by trains from the camps which were being-- you know, they were close to the front, including Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And by October, November of 1944, not only were conditions bad, they were worse, became worse, because they took away some of our barracks and made us double and triple up, you know, [? instead ?] of-- the bunks at the beginning were three-- three high, you know, with straw mattresses.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They became four or five high.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know how they held up and didn't fall over, but they did.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I guess they were next to each other so they wouldn't fall over.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And sometimes for smaller, were two or three to a-- to a bunk.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The food got to be worse, if that's possible, but it did.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We got maybe one piece of bread a week.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We did get this rotten soup-- it was frozen turnip soup== every day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Also, these-- like I said, the sanitary conditions were very bad.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They got worse because less barracks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There were no-- there no-- no washrooms.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "People started getting sick.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
